Cute comedy with Luke Wilson as an author making constant rewrites of a story acted out by Kate Hudson. Instructive for writers, entertaining for others.

This is not my rip, I found it on the net using PirateBay's tracker, so I thought it should be represented here.

Widescreen 544x288, good stereo sound.
Burn tested, runs well in both my standalone DivX players.

Optional subtitles with a character set in some non-Western language that I failed to identify. Good suggestions are welcome.
